}}# Third-party licenses

The `ton-net` native binding is one shared object per platform with its Rust
dependencies linked into it, so installing the package redistributes them. This
file carries the notices that redistribution requires, generated from the
dependency graph rather than maintained by hand.

ton-net itself is Apache-2.0, Copyright 2026 Nirapod Labs. See `LICENSE` and
`NOTICE`.

